properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 1 at 3:39AM EST until February 2 at 4:00PM EST by NWS Melbourne FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds increasing 20 to 25 kt with occasional
gusts up to 34 kt this evening and overnight. Seas building to
8 feet in the Gulf Stream.

* WHERE...Sebastian Inlet to Jupiter Inlet 0-20 nm, Flagler Beach
to Jupiter Inlet 20-60 nm.

* WHEN...From 4 PM this afternoon to 4 PM EST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Wind and wave conditions will be hazardous for small craft.
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in these conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 4 PM THIS AFTERNOON TO 4 PM EST SUNDAY
